        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Newlines are emitted for various reasons in the message grid that shouldn't be part of the emitted msg_show events. I think I went over all of these callsites in #35117. But it makes sense to extract that to a separate PR at this point with `ui_has(kUIMessages)` guards rather than waiting until that condition becomes true by default.\n\nFurther newline pruning outside of the pager may still be useful beyond that, but should first see how it is when we don't emit newlines that don't make sense in the first place (i.e. are  emitted for reasons that only make sense in the message grid).",
